gobblin.runtime.api

Class JobSpec.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.runtime.api.JobSpec.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    JobSpec

    public static class JobSpec.Builder
extends Object
    Builder for JobSpecs.

    Defaults/conventions:

    • Default jobCatalogURI is DEFAULT_JOB_CATALOG_SCHEME:
    • Convention for JobSpec URI: /config.get(ConfigurationKeys.JOB_GROUP_KEY)/config.get(ConfigurationKeys.JOB_NAME_KEY)
    • Convention for Description: config.get(ConfigurationKeys.JOB_DESCRIPTION_KEY)
    • Default version: 1
